      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every creator, small business owner, or marketer has felt it: you post something great on Instagram, your DMs explode with \"How much?\" and \"Is this available?\" messages, and by the time you reply three hours later, that hot lead has moved on. I've been there. The window between someone asking and you responding is where money slips through your fingers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-manychat"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ManyChat fixes that gap. It's an automation platform that answers DMs, captures lead info, qualifies prospects, and even processes sales — while you sleep, eat, or work on your next piece of content. If you want a deeper overview before diving in, check out our guide on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what ManyChat is",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for more context.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "In this step-by-step tutorial, I'll walk you through setting up ManyChat from scratch, building your first Instagram automation, and using its latest features to grow your audience without living inside your inbox. Let's get into it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
