            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Choose which post(s) this automation applies to — you can select a specific post or set it to trigger on all future posts. Then define the keyword. For example: if you want people to comment \"GUIDE\" to receive a free PDF, type \"GUIDE\" as the keyword. ManyChat also supports \"any comment\" triggers, which are fantastic for engagement-boosting posts.",
