      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is ManyChat Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not every tool fits every use case, but ManyChat's flexibility means it works across a surprisingly wide range of professionals:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Content Creators & Influencers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": If you use Instagram or TikTok as your primary platform, ManyChat automates the \"link in bio\" dance. Instead of telling followers to click a link, you deliver content, freebies, or product links directly in their DMs — where engagement rates are 5–10x higher than standard feed posts.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-commerce Store Owners",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": ManyChat integrates with Shopify to send abandoned cart reminders, order confirmations, and product recommendations via DM. The conversion rates on these messages consistently outperform email.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Coaches & Course Creators",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Use ManyChat to qualify leads, deliver free challenges or webinar reminders, and nurture prospects through automated sequences that feel like 1-on-1 conversations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies & Freelancers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": If you manage social media for clients, ManyChat lets you offer DM automation as a premium service. One agency owner I know charges $500/month per client just for setting up and maintaining comment-trigger automations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Local Businesses",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Restaurants, salons, gyms — any business that gets DMs asking about hours, pricing, or availability can automate those answers and free up hours every week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-manychat"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The common thread? If your audience lives on Instagram, WhatsApp, Messenger, or TikTok — and you're missing messages — ManyChat is built for you. We have a whole article on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why you should choose ManyChat",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " over building this in-house.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro Tips to Maximize Your ManyChat Results",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After building dozens of automations and watching what works, here are my top recommendations:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with comment triggers.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " They're the highest-engagement entry point. A post that says \"Comment FREE to get [X]\" converts ridiculously well because it leverages public social proof — other users see the comments piling up and join in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use tags aggressively.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Tag contacts based on which automation they entered, what answers they gave, and what links they clicked. This turns your contact list into a segmented goldmine for future campaigns.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't over-automate the conversation flow.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Keep the tone human. Use short sentences, emojis where appropriate, and give people clear buttons to tap. Long paragraphs in a DM feel like spam — even if they're automated.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set a live chat alert.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " ManyChat can notify you via the mobile app when a contact requests human help. Respond fast, and you'll close more deals.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Combine ManyChat with your email tool.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Use ManyChat to capture the email, then push it to your ESP. Chat and email together create a powerful multi-channel nurture system.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Test WhatsApp for international audiences.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you sell globally, WhatsApp automation often outperforms Instagram DMs because of higher open rates (over 90% in most markets). ManyChat handles both from the same dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/manychat-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For even more strategies, check out our dedicated ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ManyChat tips and best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l6"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " guide.",
            "marks": []
