      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start Automating Your DMs Today",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the reality: every hour your DMs sit unanswered is revenue walking out the door. ManyChat eliminates that problem with a visual, no-code builder that anyone can use — from solo creators to marketing teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The free plan lets you test everything with up to 25 contacts. That's enough to build a real automation, drive traffic to it, and see the results before you commit a single dollar. And when you're ready to scale, the Pro plan unlocks unlimited contacts, advanced features, and priority support at a price that's a fraction of what you'd pay a VA to handle DMs manually.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l7",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://manychat.partnerlinks.io/qe5octnfxtlp"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sign up for ManyChat free right here",
            "marks": [
              "l7"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and build your first automation today. It takes less time than writing one manual DM reply — and it works 24/7 forever after.",
            "marks": []
          }
