    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/manychat.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A laptop screen showing a visual chatbot flow builder with Instagram DM message bubbles, colorful automation nodes connected by lines, and a smartphone displaying a live automated conversation between a brand and a follower. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is ManyChat free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. ManyChat offers a free plan that includes up to 25 active contacts per month, 2 connected channels (Instagram, TikTok, Messenger, or Telegram), and basic automations with up to 4 active flows. It's a generous starting point that lets you build and test real automations before upgrading.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need coding skills to set up ManyChat?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not at all. ManyChat uses a visual drag-and-drop flow builder. You create conversation paths by connecting message nodes, buttons, and conditions — no technical background required. Most users build their first automation within 20 minutes of signing up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can ManyChat work with WhatsApp and TikTok?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. ManyChat supports WhatsApp Business automation (including template messages and catalog sharing) and TikTok DM automation triggered by video comments. You can manage all channels from a single dashboard, which makes cross-platform marketing much simpler.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does ManyChat capture leads from Instagram comments?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you set up a comment trigger in ManyChat, it monitors your selected posts for comments containing a specific keyword (or any comment at all). Once triggered, ManyChat automatically sends the commenter a DM with your pre-built flow — delivering links, asking questions, and collecting contact info without any manual work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
